## Not using Resend?
The endpoint is the only thing tied to Resend. If you'd rather use another provider
(SendGrid, Postmark, AWS SES) or a no-code service (Formspree, Web3Forms), swap the
`fetch(...)` call in `api/contact.js`, or point the form's action at that service.
Ask and it can be rewired.
